            <title>[FELIX-525] NPE when Ctrl-C at the &quot;Enter profile name:&quot; prompt</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-525</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;jlaskowski@dev /cygdrive/c/apps/felix&lt;br/&gt;
$ java -jar bin/felix.jar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Welcome to Felix.&lt;br/&gt;
=================&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enter profile name: (press Ctrl-C here)&lt;br/&gt;
